usage: git stow [<options>]

Stow branches and tags

    -h|--help               display help
    -r|--recursive          traverse submodules recursively
    -p|--push               mirror tags when done
                            WARNING: remote tags are deleted and replaced with local tags

- classify branches
- archive old branches (> 1 year)
- classify tags
- archive old tags (> 1 year)
- remove vtags prerelease leading zeros
- remove duplicate tags
- promote vtags in associated vbranch folder
- process orphan vtags

example:
    git stow
    git stow --push